    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor 24 Piece Deluxe Gold Panning Kit with Sluice Box was designed to give you the edge while panning for gold with portability in mind; inside the backpack, we&#039;ve included our 50&quot; Aluminum Folding Sluice Box. This lightweight, sluice box for gold panning incorporates traditional tried and true design aspects in an elongated 50 inch run out. What makes this unit different and extra handy is the ability to fold up to just 15 inches tall by 12 inches wide, easily fitting into a 5 gallon bucket as well as the included 30L canvas backpack making this ideal for beginner gold panning, day hikers, adventurers, and seasoned miner 49ers</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Gold Panning Kit with 1LB Paydirt Beginner Prospecting Tools 3 Color</h2>\n  <p>Learn how to pan for gold with this six piece ASR Outdoor gold pan kit for beginners. This exciting new prospecting starter gold panning kit includes engineered gold paydirt by professional prospector Bobby Bo. With this kit, you&#039;ll be able to learn and practice gold panning techniques at home without having to travel to a claim site.</p>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor six piece gold panning kit is an excellent option for kids and beginners who are just getting started in gold prospecting. Inside the kit, we’ve included six essential prospecting equipment tools to learn the basics of gold panning. You&#039;ll find a 12&quot; dual riffle gold pan that will help you start identifying and collecting gold. There is a 3oz gold snifter bottle that can be used to grab small gold flakes at the bottom of your gold pan, fill it with water to suck up your small gold pickers and use the included glass collection vials to safely store them.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>1LB GOLD PAYDIRT:</strong> Each beginner gold pan kit comes with a 1 pound bag of paydirt (total weight) and each pay dirt bag contains fine gold flour and coarse gold flakes in the 20-30 mesh size range; Sealed in premium resealable bag</li>\n    <li><strong>DUAL RIFFLE GOLD PAN:</strong> Best in class 12 inch gold pan has large and shallow riffle side wall, allowing better separation of gold from other material; lightweight, high contrast colors with carabiner hole</li>\n    <li>FINE GOLD RECOVERY TOOLS - (1) 3oz capacity gold snuffer bottle designed to suction pick up gold flakes and gold flour; (2) small glass vials with screw cap (1 dram and 1 2/3 dram capacity)</li>\n    <li><strong>12 INCH GOLD PAN:</strong> Rough up the gold pan before first use, seasoning the pan by washing off all factory production oils</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Materials: plastic, metal, glass, paydirt; Colors: green; Glass vial capacity: 1 dram (.065oz), 1 2/3 dram (.1oz) air tight plastic lid; Dual Riffle Gold Pan size: 12” diameter;</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/37834/ASRO_5pc_3oz_paydirt_kit_updated_2023_parent.jpg\" alt=\"Learn how to pan for gold with this six piece ASR Outdoor gold pan kit for beginners\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 5PCGOLD</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058485373</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>We partnered with Bobby Bo to bring you this fun beginner gold pan gold panning kit for beginners, so you can watch online videos and follow along at home before heading out into the field. Bobby Bo gold paydirt is packed with size 20 and size 30 mesh coarse gold flake and fine gold flour with nearly no black sand or magnetite, so you will not have to do any classification work to find your gold in the included paydirt. This bag of paydirt gold was expertly designed to practice gold prospecting techniques, not to make you rich. Bobby Bo is a gold prospecting expert who specializes in teaching classes of all ages about gold panning and gold mining.</p>\n  <p>Grab this kit for yourself, a friend or family member who enjoys outdoor activities like camping and hiking. Its fun to find gold out it nature but learning how with the proper techniques is your first step in this fun outdoor hobby.</p>\n  <p>Good luck and we hope you have a lot of fun with this paydirt gold pan gold panning kit!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ASR Outdoor 24 Piece Deluxe Gold Panning Kit with Sluice Box was designed to give you the edge while panning for gold with portability in mind; inside the backpack, we've included our 50\" Aluminum Folding Sluice Box. This lightweight, sluice box for gold panning incorporates traditional tried and true design aspects in an elongated 50 inch run out. What makes this unit different and extra handy is the ability to fold up to just 15 inches tall by 12 inches wide, easily fitting into a 5 gallon bucket as well as the included 30L canvas backpack making this ideal for beginner gold panning, day hikers, adventurers, and seasoned miner 49ers.",
